            The Thai Digital Currency and Blockchain Technology Association (TDBA) is a Thailand based, national association that connects scholars, researchers, and practice leaders in the field of digital currency, Blockchain, and Fintech Industry. It is a non-profit association committed to create an atmosphere of constructive and educational dialogue to inform the general public and to create a fact based media content about Digital Currency and blockchain technology on its course to be widely known to the world.
            <br/>
            <br/>
